# 📖 Kanji Journal

Interactive Kanji learning application built with Streamlit.

---

## 🚀 Features

- Flashcard-based kanji learning system
- Progress tracking (persistent JSON storage)
- Smart filtering of learned kanji
- Study session mode (unlearned kanji only)
- Clean interactive UI

---

## 🧠 Tech Stack

- Python
- Streamlit
- Pandas
- JSON for persistence

---

## 📊 How it works

The app loads a dataset of kanji and allows users to:
- Study kanji one by one
- Mark them as learned
- Track progress over time

---

## ▶️ Run locally

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
streamlit run app.py